    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn19.7:1.1",
          "pli": "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ usulomaṃ purisaṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ. ",
          "en": "“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw a man whose body hairs were arrows flying through the air. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.7:1.2",
          "pli": "Tassa te usū uppatitvā uppatitvā tasseva kāye nipatanti. ",
          "en": "And those arrows kept rising up and falling on his body "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.7:1.3",
          "pli": "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe … ",
          "en": "as he screamed in pain. …” … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.7:1.4",
          "pli": "eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe kāraṇiko ahosi … pe …. ",
          "en": "“That being used to be a torturer right here in Rājagaha. …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.7:1.5",
          "pli": "Sattamaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
